User Input (Streamlit)
        ↓
 Tokenizer (Hugging Face AutoTokenizer)
        ↓
Encoded Tensors (input_ids, attention_mask)
        ↓
     FinBERT (AutoModelForSequenceClassification)
        ↓
     Logits → Softmax → Probabilities
        ↓
     Argmax → Label
        ↓
      Streamlit Output (label + confidence)
